T1  - Do macroeconomic conditions and oil prices influence corporate risk-taking?
AU  - Gupta, Kartick
AU  - Krishnamurti, Chandrasekhar
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 53
SP  - 65
EP  - 86
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/12/01/
